QuestData.Title: All Natural Chews
QuestData.Description:
A huge part of larion care is providing for them and keeping them happy.
Larions need to keep their teeth sharp and healthy, and for that they need to chew. If you do not give them proper things to chew on, they can get destructive.
One of their favorite chew toys are the antlers from the cloudstriders in the nearby field. Please, collect some antlers for the pride to enjoy.
QuestData.LogDescription: Collect $1oa Cloudstrider Antlers from Gilded Cloudstriders in the Golden Pasture.
QuestData.RewardText: The larions will be ecstatic to have more antlers to chew on!
